The paper deals with LDPC code design, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of a genetic algorithm for optimization suggests a focus on optimization and search algorithms (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the practical implementation of LDPC codes, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of evolutionary algorithms and analysis of resulting codes suggests a focus on data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
